beer.beer_description:
Introducing our newest Little Creature, Squeaky Clean < 100 CAL IPA. ​

A 4% IPA with some big hop flavours including Ekuanot, Loral, Melba and Sabro which deliver a nice clean bitterness plus hints of tropical fruits and citrus. The best bit, all of this for < 100 Calories. That’s big, fruity, tropical goodness. ​

​No funny business, just Squeaky Clean deliciousness.
